# Assets Folder

This folder contains static assets for the portfolio application.

## Recommended Structure:
- images/ - Project screenshots, profile photos, etc.
- icons/ - Custom icons and SVG files
- fonts/ - Custom font files (if needed)
- documents/ - PDFs, resumes, etc.

## Notes:
- Keep image sizes optimized for web performance
- Use modern formats like WebP where supported
- Consider using a CDN for large assets in production